zogt zi, "Genye hot gehat azelekhe yinglekh; m'hot zi azoy gevolt. efsher hot zi shoyn khasene gehat."

00:11:58.752 --> 00:12:02.323
un bay mir, ver se fleg kumen zikh tsu mir shadkhenen,

00:12:02.700 --> 00:12:05.090
