00:12:11.852 --> 00:12:13.213
dos oremkeyt?

00:12:13.213 --> 00:12:16.768
mir zenen geven azelekhe vi zey. un, fleg ikh zogn, "neyn.

00:12:17.466 --> 00:12:20.193
opnarn vil ikh nit. OBESHCHAen oykh nit."

00:12:20.916 --> 00:12:22.713
 hot zi geshribn

00:12:23.355 --> 00:12:25.601
az VOT, "mayn,

00:12:25.617 --> 00:12:29.846
 zun arbet mit a yidishn mashinist," un azoy un azoy.

00:12:32.215 --> 00:12:33.882
"un UNK,

00:12:33.882 --> 00:12:36.016
ikh bet, ir zolt mir gibn ⟨a⟩ entfer;

00:12:36.016 --> 00:12:38.030
oyb Genye iz nokh a SVOBODNe,

00:12:38.037 --> 00:12:40.950
kenen mir z⟨i⟩ bakenen. efsher vet,...

00:12:41.260 --> 00:12:45.281
vayl mir gedenken dos guts vos mir hobn aykh geto- vos ir hot undz geton,

00:12:45.281 --> 00:12:50.248
un mir viln aykh opdanken nor mit gutn. vayl s'iz shtark a fayner yingl, a shtiler.

00:12:50.355 --> 00:12:52.492
er trinkt nit. a yosem.

