un mayn muter aleyn hot gezogt, "keyn Z- ZAPADNe tsi di BANDEROVTSes vil ikh nit."

00:13:06.181 --> 00:13:08.546
vayl di BANDERes zenen nokh geven demlt.

00:13:08.614 --> 00:13:10.430
zey flegn nokh oykhet hargenen.

00:13:11.702 --> 00:13:13.597
iz ongekumen di tsveyte briv,

00:13:13.597 --> 00:13:16.759
az "oyb iz Genye a farnemene, kent ir undz onshraybn,

00:13:17.018 --> 00:13:24.167
vayl s'iz aza min yingl; ven mayne tekhter zenen nokh nit khasene, volt er zey untergegangen, voltn mir im nit keynem geshadkhnt."

00:13:24.173 --> 00:13:27.609
zog ikh, "mame, oyb ire meydlekh"... un zey zenen geven shtark miese...

00:13:27.700 --> 00:13:33.229
"oyb ire meydlekh volt er geven untergegan, vet er mikh KONECHNO nit." vayl ikh fleg nokh iberkloybn oykhet.

00:13:33.690 --> 00:13:35.416
khotsh ikh bin geven orem,

00:13:35.416 --> 00:13:37.329
nor ikh hob ge- ⟨⟩...

00:13:37.943 --> 00:13:41.678
UNK yeder hot mir gemakht komplimentn az ikh bin shtark a sheyne

00:13:41.678 --> 00:13:43.407
un ikh fir zikh gut.

00:13:43.630 --> 00:13:44.825
iz hob⟨n zikh⟩,

00:13:44.825 --> 00:13:47.774
