00:13:49.468 --> 00:13:51.048
un in dem tog

00:13:51.932 --> 00:13:56.971
vos s'iz ongekumen di briv, iz gekumen a shadkhnte un hot mir geshadkhnt a yingl,

00:13:57.349 --> 00:13:58.727
vos m'hot im geshikt,

00:13:58.969 --> 00:14:03.063
 vos m'hot geshikt tsun a, eyn meydl hot geshikt tsun im,

00:14:03.222 --> 00:14:04.363
a raykhe.

00:14:04.858 --> 00:14:07.218
hot er gezogt, "di vil ikh nit,

00:14:07.218 --> 00:14:10.084
nor geyt tsu Genyen. oyb zi iz SOGLASNe,

00:14:10.528 --> 00:14:13.019
vel ikh UNK hayntikn tog."

00:14:14.123 --> 00:14:16.703
iz zi gekumen un hot ot dos gezogt. zog ikh,

00:14:16.703 --> 00:14:17.930
"er iz nit far mir."

