00:14:25.648 --> 00:14:31.416
zogt zi, "UNK ⟨shoyn⟩ nit keyn, zekhtsn, bist ⟨no⟩kh nit keyn zekhtsn yor, vos du varfst zikh nokh mit azelekhe yinglekh.

00:14:31.416 --> 00:14:33.489
me vil im azelekhe raykhe meydlekh."

00:14:35.655 --> 00:14:36.813
zog ikh,

00:14:37.309 --> 00:14:40.222
"ken ikh aykh nisht zogn. er iz nit far mir I VSЁ."

00:14:41.292 --> 00:14:44.182
un demlt hob ikh gereshet ontsushraybn ⟨a⟩ entfer

00:14:44.182 --> 00:14:45.065
im,

00:14:46.573 --> 00:14:48.507
az oyb er vil, loz er kumen.

00:14:48.835 --> 00:14:51.360
⟨un⟩ er hot gebetn nokh di fotografye mayne.

00:14:52.918 --> 00:14:54.619
hob ikh geentfert in der briv

00:14:54.619 --> 00:14:57.013
az keyn fotografye fun im darf ikh nisht;

00:14:57.188 --> 00:14:59.033
mayne ken ikh aroysshikn.

00:14:59.033 --> 00:15:03.341
oyb er tsenevet a mentshn P⟨UNK⟩ fotografye, loz er aleyn RESHAen.

00:15:03.921 --> 00:15:11.576
hot er genemen di fotografye un iz geforn keyn L'VOV tsun a khaver, oykh a yidisher, Sh⟨u⟩khman, vos er hot mit im geDRUZHet...

00:15:12.072 --> 00:15:13.939
oykhet a yosem, azoy vi er...

00:15:14.367 --> 00:15:18.898
un hot im gevizn di fotografye vos er hot bakumen fun der Ukraine ot azoy.

00:15:18.898 --> 00:15:21.093
zogt er, "oyb iz zi in lebn aza mine,

00:15:21.657 --> 00:15:25.397
medlive nit. nem OTPUSK, for, un farbreng, un breng zi."

00:15:26.314 --> 00:15:29.008
un ⟨mit⟩ azoy iz geven bay undz di ZNAKOMSTVe.

00:15:29.436 --> 00:15:31.219
punkt iz geven,

00:15:32.472 --> 00:15:37.555
oktyaber khoydesh. s'iz geven di yontoyvim undzere. mayne eltern zenen geven in shil.

00:15:37.637 --> 00:15:41.259
iz ongekumen a telegram az er hot genemen OTPUSK un er fort,

00:15:41.259 --> 00:15:43.676
mit der ZHENSHCHINe; zi hot im gefirt.

00:15:44.100 --> 00:15:46.111
 Ester hot zi oykhet geheysn,

00:15:46.699 --> 00:15:48.262
azoy vi zayn muter.

00:15:49.348 --> 00:15:50.928
 nu er iz gekumen.

00:15:51.205 --> 00:15:53.564
bin ikh im bald gefeln gevorn.

00:15:54.124 --> 00:15:57.898
a, zi hot im gezogt, "zolst visn az bay zey iz di shtub a tseklapte.

00:15:58.326 --> 00:16:03.770
zey zenen orem nokh der milkhome, nokhn krig; zey zenen geven bay di daytshn dray yor."

00:16:03.996 --> 00:16:05.842
zogt er, "dos iz gornit.

00:16:06.898 --> 00:16:09.204
⟨in marlyes, vol v-⟩ vel ikh zi onton."

00:16:09.430 --> 00:16:11.364
nu, er hot geSHUTet.

00:16:11.370 --> 00:16:12.950
un azoy iz dos geven.

00:16:13.412 --> 00:16:15.836
bald hot er mir gemakht a PREDLOZHENIE.

00:16:16.011 --> 00:16:17.338
zog ikh, "gut."

00:16:18.610 --> 00:16:20.657
emetser hot khasene,

00:16:20.657 --> 00:16:24.223
 PO RASCHЁTU un, ⟨ah⟩, emetser PO LYUBVI.

00:16:25.073 --> 00:16:27.919
zog ikh, "bay undz iz nit keyn RASCHЁТ un nit keyn LYUBOV'.

00:16:28.397 --> 00:16:30.242
keyn BOGATSTVes hob ikh nit."

00:16:30.242 --> 00:16:32.154
zogt er, "ikh freg d⟨i⟩kh nit oyf derinen."

00:16:33.257 --> 00:16:37.017
zog ikh, "un, lib⟨e⟩, vos kenen mir zikh nor tsvey teg...?"

00:16:37.017 --> 00:16:38.988
zogt er, "mir iz ge⟨da-⟩, genug,

00:16:39.366 --> 00:16:41.287
fun dem vos m'hot mir dertseylt,

00:16:41.509 --> 00:16:43.443
un ikh ze, ot azoy iz dos."

00:16:44.445 --> 00:16:47.054
nu, un tsu der vokh hobn mir zikh tseshribn.

00:16:48.040 --> 00:16:50.531
un er hot mikh bald farnemen keyn Samber.

00:16:51.246 --> 00:16:52.472
dos iz geven,

00:16:52.967 --> 00:16:54.733
dem zibetn oktyaber

00:16:54.891 --> 00:16:56.437
hobn mir zikh tseshribn,

00:16:56.562 --> 00:16:58.238
un in a por teg arum

00:16:58.238 --> 00:16:59.830
zenen mir avekgeforn,

00:17:00.460 --> 00:17:01.694
un

00:17:01.843 --> 00:17:05.162
⟨hobn mir⟩ gevoynt dortn bizkl in,

00:17:05.656 --> 00:17:09.312
KONETS finef un nayntsiktn yor, biz mir zenen aroysgeforn ater.

00:17:09.775 --> 00:17:14.814
 un, ⟨⟩, ayere eltern zenen...?

00:17:14.500 --> 00:17:16.637
mayne eltern hobn im derzen,

00:17:16.693 --> 00:17:18.678
iz er shtark gefeln gevorn.

00:17:19.426 --> 00:17:21.759
er iz geven shtark a SPOKOYNer.

00:17:22.801 --> 00:17:26.811
un m'hot im gegibn a kharakteristik az er hot nit keynem,

00:17:27.038 --> 00:17:30.255
un bald hot er ongehoybn rufn mayne eltern PAPA I MAMA,

00:17:30.463 --> 00:17:31.807
foter un muter.

00:17:32.235 --> 00:17:36.717
un zey tsun im hobn gezogt az "du bist a zun undzerer." dos iz er geven gliklekh.

00:17:38.513 --> 00:17:41.510
az ale yorn vos mir hobn mit im opgelebt dortn,

00:17:42.208 --> 00:17:45.745
tsvey mol in yor hobn mir gehat biletn oyf tsu forn.

00:17:47.322 --> 00:17:49.139
iber der gantser ROSSII

00:17:49.139 --> 00:17:52.722
hot er gekent. iz hot er nit genemen in ergets: nor keyn Bershad,

00:17:53.312 --> 00:17:55.148
vayl m'hot bay di eltern gedarft

00:17:55.148 --> 00:17:58.911
dem dakh⟨,⟩ KRASn un tsu rekht makhn, un m'hot gedarft dem eltern

00:17:58.911 --> 00:18:01.940
ZABOR. m'hot gedarft di eltern epes ot azoy.

00:18:01.940 --> 00:18:05.405
un akhuts der⟨inen lozn⟩ di eltern hobn fargenign fun zeyere eyniklekh,

00:18:05.445 --> 00:18:07.346
vos zenen gekumen atin tsu.

00:18:08.382 --> 00:18:10.546
er hot shtark lib gehat di eltern.

00:18:11.993 --> 00:18:13.546
un zey im.

00:18:15.157 --> 00:18:16.157
⟨t-⟩

00:18:15.300 --> 00:18:18.944
un di eltern zenen geb- geblibn in Bershad?

00:18:17.713 --> 00:18:22.820
 in Bershad, vayl dortn iz, hobn zey gehat zeyer voynung. dort iz geven di bobe.

00:18:23.822 --> 00:18:26.600
un zey hobn keyn mol nit getrakht fun aroystsuforn.

00:18:27.838 --> 00:18:32.574
di shtub hobn zey gekent far dem gelt, vos zey hobn azoy fil yorn zi gebovet,

00:18:32.614 --> 00:18:37.181
un fun di o, fun der bombe, ⟨zi⟩ fleg zikh shtendik opzetsn, biz hayntikn tog.

00:18:37.241 --> 00:18:40.218
s- di shtub shteyt nokh; ⟨v-⟩ s'voynen dortn goyim.

00:18:41.575 --> 00:18:45.737
nor vos me leygt atin nit arayn, say vi zetst zi zikh.

00:18:46.890 --> 00:18:54.022
hobn zey gezogt, "neyn. ot dos iz undzer zeyde's, dos iz undzer bobe's, dos iz undzere eltern, un ot do darfn mir shtarbn."

00:18:54.332 --> 00:18:58.471
ir zet, di bobe take hot men aroysgetrogn fun der shtub vos zi hot ⟨mitshtayert⟩.

00:18:58.471 --> 00:19:03.574
un zey zenen avekgeforn keyn Erets-Yisroel, derfar vos der bruder iz avekgeforn.

00:19:03.765 --> 00:19:06.594
hobn zey shoyn nit gehat keynem, un keyn yidn iz shoyn nit geblibn.

00:19:06.887 --> 00:19:09.868
s'zenen di letste yidn avekgeforn fun der gas,

00:19:11.511 --> 00:19:15.126
zenen zey avekgeforn atin tsu. un dortn hobn zey gelebt,

00:19:13.232 --> 00:19:14.390
ven d-...

00:19:15.392 --> 00:19:17.107
azoy vi a koridortshikl,

00:19:17.502 --> 00:19:18.981
bay a balebos.

00:19:19.375 --> 00:19:21.394
shreklekh a shlekhter mentsh!

00:19:21.231 --> 00:19:23.233
vu? in Yisroel?

00:19:22.345 --> 00:19:23.503
in Yis- yo.

00:19:24.387 --> 00:19:29.055
un ven zenen zey aroys fun, fun Bershad? ven zenen zey geforn keyn Yisroel?

00:19:27.778 --> 00:19:29.701
in eyn un nayntsiktn yor.

00:19:29.500 --> 00:19:31.586
in eyn un nayntsikstn yor?

00:19:32.115 --> 00:19:35.259
un ir zent dervayl geven in...?

00:19:34.360 --> 00:19:36.964
un ikh bin geven in, Samber.

00:19:35.259 --> 00:19:37.323
in ⟨Lemberg⟩? in Samber.

00:19:36.964 --> 00:19:41.121
ikh bin geven dortn. ⟨ikh b- ikh bin in,⟩ mir zenen eyne geblibn.

00:19:41.380 --> 00:19:44.276
der zun mayner hot oykhet getrakht tsu forn ⟨k-⟩ atin,

00:19:44.417 --> 00:19:50.773
nor dernokh dem, az ⟨es,⟩ m'hot gegibn a zog az m'hot, di yidn kenen forn keyn, EVROPe,

00:19:51.252 --> 00:19:52.950
hot di shnur ongehoybn,

00:19:53.175 --> 00:19:54.494
"Izye,

00:19:55.690 --> 00:19:57.878
lomir forn keyn GERMANye,

00:19:58.305 --> 00:20:01.522
vayl me shraybt azelekhe briv, vi m'helft yidn,

00:20:01.933 --> 00:20:04.475
un ⟨der,⟩ YAZYK,

00:20:04.515 --> 00:20:08.846
azoy vi mir veysn do nit, azoy iz dortn, nor dort iz dos lebn nokh shverer.

00:20:09.848 --> 00:20:11.496
lomir forn ater."

00:20:12.160 --> 00:20:15.310
nu, hot er zikh SOGLASHAet, un ikh, far der tsayt,

00:20:15.310 --> 00:20:17.638
ikh, az ikh hob derhert az er fort ater,

00:20:18.015 --> 00:20:21.429
iz demlt hob ikh bakumen di ARITMIYA,

00:20:21.429 --> 00:20:23.662
un GIPERTONIYA.

00:20:23.871 --> 00:20:26.193
kh'hob shtark geveynt; kh'hob nit gevolt.

00:20:26.925 --> 00:20:30.425
kh'hob gezogt, "vi azoy? s'iz a bushe far,

00:20:30.672 --> 00:20:33.045
far dem prakht fun undzere gehargete,

00:20:33.152 --> 00:20:35.157
az mir zoln forn atin tsu.

00:20:35.157 --> 00:20:37.298
vi azoy kent ir? ikh veys nit."

00:20:37.523 --> 00:20:40.419
hobn zey ongehoybn az se baytn zikh di tsaytn,

00:20:41.083 --> 00:20:45.650
un ot o di, daytshn vos zenen geblibn, di yunge,

00:20:46.770 --> 00:20:48.350
zenen nit shuldik:

00:20:49.183 --> 00:20:51.850
tate-mame zindikn un kinder kumen op.

00:20:51.850 --> 00:20:53.719
un FAKTICHESKe azoy iz dos,

00:20:53.719 --> 00:20:57.007
az itstert ot o di o POSOBIE vos mir POLUCHAen,

00:20:57.165 --> 00:20:59.015
iz umshuldike mentshn

00:21:00.118 --> 00:21:01.900
helfn undz, azoy.

00:21:02.970 --> 00:21:05.529
nu, ot azoy hobn mir zikh gereshet.

00:21:06.953 --> 00:21:08.257
zent ir in

00:21:08.257 --> 00:21:09.664
tsvey un nayntsik,

00:21:10.497 --> 00:21:13.883
 in finef un nayntsikstn yor zent ir ahergekumen?

00:21:12.302 --> 00:21:19.687
 in DEKABR' khoydesh. mir hobn gehat anketes. zey hobn gevolt in eynem mit undz, mir zoln oykhet. hob ikh gezogt, "neyn."

00:21:19.963 --> 00:21:22.353
hobn zey gebetn, "nemt anketes;

00:21:22.478 --> 00:21:24.986
ir vet nit veln forn, zitst ⟨ir⟩ dortn."

00:21:25.093 --> 00:21:30.959
nor dos lebn in der Ukraine iz gevorn shtark shver. nit arbetn, un nit keyn pensye, nit gornit.

00:21:32.704 --> 00:21:35.814
un s'iz geshtanen di frage: mir zenen eltere mentshn,

00:21:35.814 --> 00:21:41.743
di shvester voynt... di tokhter mayne... in L'VOV, in ⟨a⟩ OBSHCHEZHITIE. keyn kvartir hob ikh ir nit gekent koyfn.

00:21:44.044 --> 00:21:45.492
hot der zun ongehoybn,

00:21:45.492 --> 00:21:51.058
"mame, az ir vet kumen keyn, Daytshland, keyn atin, keyn, tsun undz,

00:21:51.975 --> 00:21:58.517
vestu zen vi s'vet aykh zayn gringer, un s'vet undz zayn gringer vos dos eynikl ayers, dos eyntsike, vet khotsh hobn a PRITULOK.

00:21:58.517 --> 00:22:02.949
az mir zenen yunge mentshn, mir darfn nokh lernen dem YAZYK un mir darfn,

00:22:02.949 --> 00:22:04.029
arbetn,

00:22:04.029 --> 00:22:06.549
un mir lozn zi iber oyf fremde mentshn."

00:22:08.530 --> 00:22:12.103
 say vi hobn mir nit gevolt. mir hobn zikh nit gekent opreshen.

00:22:13.339 --> 00:22:18.429
nu, un dernokh zenen mir shoyn geforn keyn Kiev nemen, di anketes.

00:22:20.072 --> 00:22:23.724
iz shoyn geven azelekhe shreklekhe otsheredn, nor

00:22:23.724 --> 00:22:26.304
di tokhter mayne iz tsugegan tsu dem daytsh,

00:22:26.304 --> 00:22:27.795
tsu, vos er hot dizhurevet,

00:22:28.527 --> 00:22:30.107
un mentshn,

00:22:30.197 --> 00:22:31.215
yidn,

00:22:31.215 --> 00:22:36.570
⟨, s'iz⟩ geven khmares. m'iz geshtanen in di otsheredn un m'hot zikh farshribn.

00:22:36.576 --> 00:22:39.320
khadoshimvayz hot men gevart oyf di anketes.

00:22:40.170 --> 00:22:46.542
iz zi tsugegan un zogt, "mayne elt- mayn muter iz geven in lager bay di daytshn, un zi hot a dokument."

00:22:47.342 --> 00:22:54.575
⟨,⟩ der dokument... "geyt epes az, ⟨,⟩ VNE OCHEREDI, zol zi POLUCHen, di ankete." iz er tsugegan un hot mikh aroysgenemen fun ale

00:22:54.683 --> 00:22:56.080
un arayngefirt

00:22:56.080 --> 00:22:57.427
di ershte atin tsu,

00:22:57.602 --> 00:23:01.429
un m'hot mir gegibn di anketes. hob ikh gevolt fun iret vegn oykhet,

00:23:01.429 --> 00:23:02.367
fun der to-...

00:23:02.367 --> 00:23:05.477
zogn zey, "zi iz shoyn a, UNK, SH- SOVERSHENNOLETN⟨YAYA⟩,

00:23:05.837 --> 00:23:07.957
darf zi zayn in OBSHCHe otshered."

00:23:08.233 --> 00:23:11.720
